Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治5年9月\N新橋和橫濱間的鐵路開通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.27,0:01:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連接世界船隻群集的\N橫濱和日本首都東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所需時間不超過1個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從英國引進的蒸氣火車頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可牽引八節車廂以\N時速40公里的速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正可說是文明開化的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.23,0:02:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其利用者乃是以\N經營國外貿易的商人為主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在當時 因為傳言火車頭\N所發出的火會引起火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 鐵道大部份\N都被設計在海岸邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.51,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因此 天晴時可以看到\N遠方的下總群山和富士山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十二話\N第一次的蒸氣火車仰天大事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火車進站了 不快點會來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出門了還在磨蹭的是誰啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有備無患呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是應有的觀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！我可不是自願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是因為你每天在道場工作很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.76,0:03:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾也該讓你散散心\N才讓你坐坐蒸氣火車呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還得謝謝我呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 好了 兩個別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個夠了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光吵嘴也無濟於事 對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然來了就開心地玩吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦 這麼多人聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是來看火車\N不該會這麼多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包了一整車廂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面裝的好像是以前的金幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是現在英國的貿易商人\N正在上特別車廂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然漂亮蒸氣火車真是華麗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豁出去花這錢是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾大玩一下也是需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了橫濱一定要去吃\N西洋的甜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種叫秀可拉多的甜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後大家一起照照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有 還有 要看看洋裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅紗 更紗 真好聽的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到了 誰是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 無憂無慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以說師傅無憂無慮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火車就要開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請送行的人下車等待發車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有意見的話\N現在下車也可以哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.15,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰買給你的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.22,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看啊！很貴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這票一張要花一塊錢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要感謝我的慷慨大方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下車！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要下車！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要下車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 把左之助攔住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定是被狐貍給迷惑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一醒 人已在糞坑裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.67,0:06:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.91,0:06:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不照相\N那東西會吸取人的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還相信那種事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我問你為什麼\N這麼大的東西會動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說了嘛\N是蒸氣的動力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒸氣不是就開水的蒸氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是白癡啊 水壺的蒸氣怎麼\N推動這麼重的東西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是白癡啊\N火車頭哪裏是水壺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 你好好地說明看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…名叫史迪文生的人\N他燒開水時發現壺蓋被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看火車頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去看看駕駛室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘客要乖乖地坐著別搗蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小氣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是車掌 不得了了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.91,0:07:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說 馬上把火車停住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出事了 必須馬上停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停車？是什麼大事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狐貍精和水壺\N是哪一個說不通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是水壺！是狐貍精！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說水壺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼嘴硬就叫劍心來評評理吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 在下也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別座的客人說 馬上停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.09,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點奇怪 你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 回話啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你停車…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是假的\N一定有什麼陰謀 不能停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小子！\N果然剛才應該把你丟出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.14,0:09:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 快停車\N否則把這小鬼丟下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是金幣！一定是想搶金幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多嘴！把嘴巴閉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是一名乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,途中若是被你停住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待的橫濱觀光就去不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想把連結器打開是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你不像是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.11,0:11:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真累 這梯子真累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 做生意 當強盜\N都很難隨心所欲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:11:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要…請你退場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.56,0:12:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准碰！不准碰你的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還真難對付\N不過到此為止了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住！小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他 沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達預定地之前\N把特別車廂切離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真久 禰彥和劍心在磨蹭什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.64,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如我所說 他們兩個現在醒了\N正在糞坑裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真固執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了 劍心他….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心他….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎮定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連結器打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來就是等待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆 大庭廣眾之下\N搬給人家看是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警衛的人數都被知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託人家來搶是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪  車速還沒慢下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 這叫作人算不如天算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 開我玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多危險啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是叫你躲一邊看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.69,0:14:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N我可是神谷活心流代理師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大意失荊州喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我只是個小孩子\N身體輕可是足以自傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死心吧 來呀 來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我們坐同一輛車\N可是你的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別高興的太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是海盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好多船啊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不許動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你們搗蛋 計劃有些亂\N不過 也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.89,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把金幣運完之前\N你們就在這乖乖等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫你不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.87,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我多費手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖地不亂來 我不會動粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是紳士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不喜歡看到血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜 到這地步 萬事已遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想幹嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不許動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.90,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…放手小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋 乖乖地離開這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑 夥計們幹掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡快離開這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.79,0:18:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助和薰小姐弄連接器\N禰彥麻煩你去幫機關手的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋 看你們打算\N怎樣從這裏逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻礙全部清除乾淨為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流…龍槌閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快 趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能追的快追 別讓火車逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.71,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是蒸氣火車 船可追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙到底是誰….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 真是太好了 劍心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰小姐很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 惹人厭的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在那兒抱著腿發抖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.12,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說無論如何都要我們收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.96,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是謝謝你 多虧你的相救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.73,0:20:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼用 就讓薰小姐作主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 這麼多的錢….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要的話 我拿嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家要不要照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我不要 靈魂會被吸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在說 那是迷信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要說幾次才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.19,0:20:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭 每拍一張壽命就縮短一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是惡魔的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 你們兩個別再吵嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜 擺那什麼姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話 照片就拍不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼嘛 一點也沒影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.21,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拍嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 我要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要拉我的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個好了沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要…

